<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.209055>
    dc:description "FIGURE 6. Phalangopsina dubia (Bolivar, 1900). A, right scape, anterior side; B, maxillary palpus, last joint; C, outer apical spurs of hind tibia; D – F, male genitalia, dorsal (D), ventral (E), lateral (F); G – H, female copulatory papilla, dorsal (G), lateral (H). Abbreviations: see text p. ***. Scales 1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/209055/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.209057>
    dc:description "FIGURE 8. Phalangopsina bolivari Desutter-Grandcolas n. sp. (A – G) and Phalangopsina chopardi Desutter-Grandcolas n. sp. (H – L). A, H, scape, anterior side; B, maxillary palpus; C, D, I, apical spurs of hind tibia, inner (C, I), outer (D); E, J, female subgenital plate; F, G, K, L, female copulatory papilla, dorsal (F, K), lateral (G, L). Abbreviations, see text p. ***. Scales 1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/209057/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

